        <title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Cooperative Round-Robin Scheduler. </para>

<para>A simple task scheduler that manages a fixed number of Tasks. Scheduling is cooperative, meaning task execution is done by calling a work cycle function that must return into the scheduler as fast as possible. Tasks in running state are called round-robion sequentially.</para>

